                                                Welcome to My Express API
This api is extirely developed with node js without any frontend framework like React or Angular

All `POST` endpoints return Json reponse and `GET`, returning templates

`GET /`
    This return the verification/sign in page. User is expected to fill in his/her credentials for verification in order to get to the homepage.

`POST /`
    Returns null(Not Implemeted)


`GET /verify`
    This endpoint redirects to the `GET /`

`POST /verify`
    Accompanied with dataset in Json format of {"email":USER_EMAIL,"password":USER_PASSWORD}, a request to this endpoint returns the homepage after a SUCCESSFULL verification.